-- PUREPALATE 2.0 --

-- Pages --
/                       
/findrecipes - This page will enable the user to find recipes based on 
an ingredient, or various health categories. Nutritional info will be provided
for these recipes. 

/buildrecipes - This page will enable the user to create their own recipes 
and save them to their account. Nutritional info will also be provided for 
these recipes. 

/foodinfo - This page will enable the user to get information about various
foods and dishes via ChatGPT API. 

/about - This page will provide the user with information about this project and
its inspiration. 




PRISMA NOTES

1. After making adjustments to the database in schema.prisma, run npx
prisma migrate to commit your changes to the actual SQLITE database. 
